---
// Features/Differentials Section Component
---

<section class="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Por que escolher a HJLOG?</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Segurança e tecnologia integradas para garantir a melhor experiência logística.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">shield_lock</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Segurança Total</h3>
          <p>Gerenciamento de risco avançado e seguro total da carga.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2 -->
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">speed</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Agilidade</h3>
          <p>Processos otimizados para reduzir o tempo de trânsito.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">support_agent</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Suporte 24h</h3>
          <p>Equipe dedicada para atender suas demandas a qualquer hora.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 4 -->
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">smartphone</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>App Exclusivo</h3>
          <p>Tecnologia na palma da mão para acompanhar tudo.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features {
    width: 100%;
    padding: var(--space-20) 0;
    background-color: var(--background-light);
  }

  .dark .features {
    background-color: var(--background-dark);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: var(--container-max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-4);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .container {
      padding-left: var(--container-padding-tablet);
      padding-right: var(--container-padding-tablet);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .container {
      padding-left: var(--container-padding-desktop);
      padding-right: var(--container-padding-desktop);
    }
  }

  .header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--text-primary-light);
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    h2 {
      font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    }
  }

  .dark h2 {
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: var(--text-secondary-light);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .dark .subtitle {
    color: var(--text-tertiary-dark);
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .feature-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    background-color: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }

  .dark .feature-card {
    background-color: var(--surface-dark);
    border-color: var(--border-dark);
  }

  .icon-wrapper {
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    background-color: var(--primary-light);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--text-primary-light);
  }

  .dark .icon-wrapper {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .icon-wrapper .material-symbols-outlined {
    font-size: 24px;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--text-primary-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }

  .dark h3 {
    color: var(--white);
  }

  p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary-light);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  }

  .dark p {
    color: var(--text-tertiary-dark);
  }
</style>
